"{\"uid\": \"cnbc.com-2024-01-12-corona-maker-ab-inbev-to-have-first-ever-sponsorship-with-the-olympics.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  In this article  Anheuser-Busch InBevhas scored a sponsorship for the upcoming Olympic Games, making it the first beer brand to ever sponsor the event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 33, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AB_InBev\", \"score\": 0.8376917738670673, \"rank\": 0.1937564780366673, \"text\": \"Anheuser-Busch\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AB_InBev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AB_InBev\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee announced its worldwide partnership with the world's biggest brewing company on Friday, saying the team-up will stretch from the upcoming Paris 2024 Summer games to Los Angeles 2028 Summer games.\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 159, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 329, \"end\": 339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.621525935084782e-23, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC specifically highlighted Corona Cero as the beer of choice for the partnership.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 392, \"end\": 395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.420987114937696e-18, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Corona Cero, one of AB InBev's non-alcoholic beers,contains less than 0.5% alcohol by volume, according to the company's website.\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The low-alcohol space is a great opportunity,\\\" Doukeris told CNBC's Arabile Gumede on Friday.\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 701, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999693046, \"rank\": 2.715536060070861e-11, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doukeris also noted that the beer industry hasremained resilientamid global supply chain concerns.\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has a \\\"characteristic as a category that is incredible, which is beer is local,\\\" Doukeris said.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We source our ingredients locally, sometimes we grow our ingredients locally, from barley, hops ... sometimes the bottles, the cans, [are] local as well.\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Beer usually does not travel a lot because we have breweries in the local communities where we operate.\\\"\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This partnership could be a comeback of sorts for AB InBev, which previously announced that it would be focusing its marketing efforts on sporting and music events.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1326, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That pivot came after the company faced backlash for its partnership with transgender influence Dylan Mulvaney, including conservative boycotts.\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"score\": 0.9999966384829915, \"rank\": 3.347896733104385e-06, \"text\": \"Dylan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bud Light sales slumped in the wake of the protests, giving Modelo Especial center stage as thebest-selling beerin the U.S. last May.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1473, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anheuser-Busch_brands\", \"score\": 0.9992012496552479, \"rank\": 0.0007993888568074701, \"text\": \"Bud Light\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anheuser-Busch_brands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anheuser-Busch_brands\"}, {\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grupo_Modelo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Modelo Especial\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grupo_Modelo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grupo_Modelo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Disclosure: CNBC parent NBCUniversal owns NBC Sports and NBC Olympics.\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1620, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999693046, \"rank\": 2.715536060070861e-11, \"text\": \"CNBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1632, \"end\": 1644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9999999900171588, \"rank\": 9.982269661497464e-09, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpe